articles.title: Taiwan president to visit US but no word on House Speaker meeting - Reuters.com
articles.description: Taiwan President Tsai Ing-wen will make sensitive stopovers in the United States on her way to and from Central America that China's foreign ministry condemned on Tuesday, but Taipei would not confirm a meeting with U.S. House Speaker Kevin McCarthy.
